quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  75,31,He neither believed nor prayed
  75,32,But he belied and turned away
  75,33,Then he departed Unto his house hold conceitedly
  75,34,Woe Unto thee; woe
  75,35,"Again, woe Unto thee, woe"
  75,36,Deemest man that he is to be left uncontrolled
  75,37,Was he not a sperm of emission emitted
  75,38,Then he became a clot; then He created him and formed him
  75,39,"And made of him the two sexes, male and female"
  75,40,Is not That One then Able to quicken the dead